5.	Deployment: Apply secure configurations and monitoring.
6.	Maintenance: Patch vulnerabilities and continuously monitor security.
•	Importance in Fintech:
•	Reduces risk of cyberattacks.
•	Ensures compliance with fintech regulations.
•	Integrates security into everyday development practices.



